## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Build backend query tests in `backend/tests/analytics.test.ts`.

### Manual Verification
1. Open the **Analytics** page.
2. Confirm the orange banner appears at the top showing the count of products with missing cost prices.
3. Click the banner link; confirm it takes you to the Inventory page pre-filtered to those specific products.
4. Go back to Analytics, hover over the "Net Profit" metric card, and click it.
5. Confirm the drawer slides in from the right showing the exact math (Revenue components, COGS list, Expenses list, Net Profit).
